<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="text-align: right;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" style="" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">Dear&nbsp;<span class="il">Parents</span>,&nbsp;<br></font></div><div><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">&nbsp;</font></div><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">We are pleased to announce that the 2018-19&nbsp;<span class="il">Parent</span>&nbsp;Satisfaction&nbsp;<span class="il">Survey</span>&nbsp;is now live and will remain open until 20 January 2019.</font></div><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">You can access the&nbsp;<span class="il">survey</span>&nbsp;here: <a href="http://parentsurvey.nordanglia.com/survey/selfserve/5a0/181000?=Nord%20Anglia,Parents&amp;wave=y2019" target="_blank" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://parentsurvey.nordanglia.com/survey/selfserve/5a0/181000?%3DNord%2520Anglia,Parents%26wave%3Dy2019&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1544085411423000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGxflgNZd6p7p_8AXbW5jDbwW4DCA" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">2018-19 NAE&nbsp;<span class="il">Parent</span>&nbsp;Satisfaction&nbsp;<span class="il">Survey</span></a></font></div><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">The&nbsp;<span class="il">survey</span>&nbsp;is accessible through a PC, Mac, tablet, iPad, or smartphone and should take you no longer than 15 minutes to complete. Kindly note that the&nbsp;<span class="il">survey</span>&nbsp;must be 100% accomplished in one sitting. Otherwise, your form will not be counted and recorded.&nbsp;</font></div><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">Each family should respond once on behalf of all your children. If you wish to share specific feedback, please provide that feedback in the open comment boxes at the end of the&nbsp;<span class="il">survey</span>.</font></div><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">We want your honest views, so your responses are anonymous and will be combined with those of other&nbsp;<span class="il">parents</span>&nbsp;at our school. We are constantly looking for ways to improve our school and your feedback is vital to this process. Our annual&nbsp;<span class="il">parent</span>&nbsp;satisfaction&nbsp;<span class="il">survey</span>&nbsp;helps us better understand how we are performing in key areas, including what we are doing well and any opportunities for improvement.&nbsp;</font></div><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">Our aim is to continue providing the best possible educational experience for your child. We encourage you to participate in the&nbsp;<span class="il">survey</span>. The results are used to inform our strategy for continuous improvement. Therefore, the more&nbsp;<span class="il">parents</span>&nbsp;we hear from, the more confident we can be that our action plans respond to your views.</font></div><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">I would like to highlight and share with you some results and actions from last year's&nbsp;<span class="il">survey</span>;</font></div><div><ul><li style="margin-left: 15px;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">NAIS Manila obtained the highest&nbsp;<span class="il">parent</span>&nbsp;<span class="il">survey</span>&nbsp;response rate across all NAE schools. Your active support is invaluable to NAIS Manila's growth and is very much appreciated. We are looking forward to continuing this optimism from our&nbsp;<span class="il">parent</span>&nbsp;body this year.&nbsp;</font></li><li style="margin-left: 15px;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">A number of&nbsp;<span class="il">parents</span>&nbsp;agreed there was a need for improvement with indoor facilities. And over the summer, we have made changes to the ground floor area to now include a theatre / performing arts space, a dedicated Admissions Suite to comfortably handle administrative transactions and also to properly entertain new student enquiries. And to celebrate our inclusion in the Nord Anglia Education Global family, we have also revamped the Reception area to include our new school branding and philosophy, new furniture for better seating and waiting area, and also provide local and global video updates on the tv screen.&nbsp;</font></li><li style="margin-left: 15px;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">Additional investments in IT have also been made to ensure that more children within the school have access to IT equipment.&nbsp;</font></li></ul></div><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">Rest assured that all comments we receive from you are&nbsp;thoughtfully considered and deemed high priorities.</font></div><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">We will share the results of this year's&nbsp;<span class="il">survey</span>&nbsp;during the Third Term.</font></div><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">Many thanks for your participation, we look forward to hearing your views.</font></div><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">Kind regards</font></div></div><div><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><div dir="ltr" class="m_-7403819778400144826m_8803738615813968388m_7669807245126991333gmail-m_9095505602175167582gmail_signature"><div dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif"><b>David Kirkham</b></font></div><div dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">Principal</font></div><div><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Nord Anglia International School Manila</span></div></div></div></div></div><div style="text-align: left;"><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;"><font style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" style="" size="2">+63 (2) 519 5799</font></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" style="" size="2">www.naismanila.edu.ph</font></p></div></div>]]></td>
